text: The Disappearance of Finbar is a 1996 Irish Swedish mystery drama movie directed by Sue Clayton and starring Jonathan Rhys Meyers, Colin Farrell, Lorraine Pilkington. It was distributed by Channel 4 Films. ==Other websites== * Category:1996 drama movies Category:1996 mystery movies Category:Irish drama movies Category:Swedish drama movies
